com.ecmdeveloper.eds.model

Class Choice

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ecmdeveloper.eds.model.Choice

  • public class Choice
extends Object
    This class represents an item in a choice list. There a two types of choice list items:
    • An item representing one value, either a string of an integer.
    • An item representing a leaf in a hierarchical choice list (currently only supported by Content Navigator)
    Both types are supported by this class.
    Author:
    Ricardo Belfor
